06:29.220 --> 06:31.980
 development lasts the entire lifespan.

06:31.980 --> 06:35.040
 From the time you're conceived until the time you die,

06:35.040 --> 06:36.720
 you are developing, you are changing,

06:36.720 --> 06:40.600
