46:33.500 --> 46:35.780
 Some people are staying ketogenic for long periods of time.

46:35.780 --> 46:37.420
 Some people, six days on, one day off.

46:37.420 --> 46:39.700
 So there's a huge variation there.

46:39.700 --> 46:43.340
 The point is that carbohydrates, starchy carbohydrates

46:43.340 --> 46:45.820
