 It all starts to fit together

47:29.740 --> 47:31.560
 in ways that make a lot of sense

47:31.560 --> 47:33.640
 once you understand just kind of the core elements

47:33.640 --> 47:34.700
 of what the hormones are

47:34.700 --> 47:36.980
 and the variety of tissues that they work on.

