 for short periods of time,

1:30:31.380 --> 1:30:34.180
 anywhere from 20 minutes to 30 minutes,

1:30:34.180 --> 1:30:38.980
 where the temperature is 80 degrees Celsius

1:30:38.980 --> 1:30:40.340
 to 100 degrees Celsius,

